That beginning?

55:39.669 --> 55:43.571
And the earth was
a formless void...

55:43.640 --> 55:46.734
and darkness covered
the face of the deep.

55:50.280 --> 55:52.805
But the darkness wasn't empty.

55:52.882 --> 55:56.875
It was full of creatures.
Full of demons.

55:58.588 --> 56:03.616
<i>And they had seven keys</i>
<i>formed into a circle...</i>

56:03.693 --> 56:08.153
<i>to focus the power of the cosmos</i>
<i>into their hands...</i>

56:08.231 --> 56:11.291
<i>until God stepped forth</i>
<i>and said,</i>

56:11.368 --> 56:14.565
<i>"Let there be light."</i>

56:14.637 --> 56:17.071
<i>And there was light.</i>

56:17.140 --> 56:21.907
<i>And He scattered the demons...</i>
<i>and He scattered the keys...</i>

56:21.978 --> 56:24.742
all across the universe.

56:24.814 --> 56:30.446
Then we fast-forward about
two or three million millennia.

56:30.520 --> 56:32.920
Now the demons are back.

56:32.989 --> 56:35.321
They got six of the keys.

56:35.392 --> 56:40.295
