the seventh key here on earth.

56:40.363 --> 56:44.493
<i>To save it, God filled it</i>
<i>with the blood of a carpenter...</i>

56:44.567 --> 56:48.264
who was being crucified
by the Romans...

56:48.338 --> 56:50.898
and gave it to a thief
named Sirach.

56:50.974 --> 56:54.808
<i>The blood ins... inside...</i>
<i>is that...</i>

56:54.878 --> 56:58.006
Some of it. Yeah.

56:58.081 --> 57:00.777
<i>It gets used, you see.</i>

57:00.850 --> 57:03.842
