the artery here.

57:09.759 --> 57:13.820
<i>Most of what's in here now</i>
<i>belonged to a soldier</i>
<i>named Dickerson.</i>

57:13.897 --> 57:18.891
Gave it to me in France.
August 23, 1917.

57:18.968 --> 57:21.801
Funny how you remember
the big dates.

57:21.871 --> 57:26.308
Jesus, that...
would make you, uh...

57:26.376 --> 57:29.277
What happens when you
run out of blood?

57:32.215 --> 57:35.207
- They bring back the darkness.
- Just like that?

57:36.886 --> 57:38.820
Just like that.

57:42.358 --> 57:44.292
So...

57:46.663 --> 57:48.756
now you know.

57:48.832 --> 57:51.062
You feel better?

57:54.537 --> 57:57.165
[Sighs]

58:00.777 --> 58:03.211
God, I wish I had
that bottle of vodka now.

58:10.553 --> 58:12.987
I guess I owe you
an apology, Brayker.

58:13.056 --> 58:15.650
You really got
some balls, man.

58:17.227 --> 58:19.661
You're a fucking hero.

58:19.729 --> 58:21.959
Where's Danny?

58:22.031 --> 58:25.125
What?
Find him.

58:25.201 --> 58:27.499
<i>I'm gonna check</i>
<i>in my room.</i>
<i>I'll look in my room.</i>

58:27.570 --> 58:29.504
<i>Danny!</i>
I'll stay here.

58:32.575 --> 58:34.805
Danny?

58:36.246 --> 58:39.181
Danny?
