59:14.717 --> 59:17.151
<i>I can help you.</i>

59:21.991 --> 59:25.552
<i>You want Paris, Rome, Athens?</i>
<i>You got it.</i>

59:27.397 --> 59:31.163
<i>Course, if you don't help me,</i>
<i>that's a whole other picture.</i>

59:34.604 --> 59:39.200
<i>Come on, let's be real.</i>
<i>Brayker isn't gonna get you</i>
<i>out of here, okay?</i>

59:39.275 --> 59:41.937
<i>Brayker can't even</i>
<i>get himself out.</i>

59:43.746 --> 59:47.546
<i>Little secret:</i>
<i>The man's dead meat.</i>

59:47.617 --> 59:51.451
<i>And if you stick with him,</i>
<i>you're gonna end up</i>
<i>the same way.</i>

59:51.521 --> 59:54.718
[Gasping]

59:54.791 --> 59:57.521
<i>Check this out.</i>

59:57.594 --> 01:00:00.722
<i>I hate to even think about it.</i>

01:00:00.797 --> 01:00:05.734
<i>It's a simple deal, Jeryline:</i>
<i>You let me in, I let you out.</i>

01:00:08.304 --> 01:00:10.772
Horrible, isn't it?
[Gasps]

01:00:10.840 --> 01:00:13.308
You know, it doesn't
have to be unpleasant.

01:00:13.376 --> 01:00:15.901
